## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="76042-102">输入的模式<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>由其<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="76042-102">The input mode for an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> is determined by its <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="76042-103">默认值输入的模式就是指示定义语法的声音<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>将与语音输入匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="76042-103">The default input mode is Voice, which indicates that the grammar defined by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> will match speech input.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="76042-104">Dtmf 模式指示语法将匹配而不是语音双音多频率 (DTMF) 铃音。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="76042-104">The Dtmf mode indicates that a grammar will match Dual-Tone Multi-Frequency (DTMF) tones instead of speech.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="76042-105">有 16 DTMF 铃音，12 种通常位于大多数电话。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="76042-105">There are 16 DTMF tones, 12 of which are commonly found on most telephones.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="76042-106">当你创建<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>对象<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>对象将匹配的指定的输入类型<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A>属性，获取的实例<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarMode>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="76042-106">When you create a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object from an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object will match the type of input specified by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> property, which gets an instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarMode>.</span></span>  



## Examples  

```csharp  
string srgsDocumentFile = Path.Combine(Path.GetTempPath(), "srgsDocumentFile.xml");  
SrgsDocument document = null;  
GrammarBuilder builder = null;  
Grammar grammar = null;  

Choices firstThree = new Choices(new string[] {"1", "2", "3"});  
Choices nextThree = new Choices(new string[] {"4", "5", "6"});  
Choices lastThree = new Choices(new string[] {"7", "8", "9"});  

Choices keyPadChoices = new Choices(new GrammarBuilder[] {firstThree, nextThree, lastThree, new Choices("0")});  

builder = new GrammarBuilder(keyPadChoices);  
document = new SrgsDocument(builder);  

document.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Dtmf;  
grammar = new Grammar(document);   
```
